    }
  ],
  "bodyHtml": "<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Why this new feature?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Many carriers deliver on Saturdays and Sundays, but we&#39;ve historically shown delivery times in business days only. You can now reflect weekend operations in your delivery promise so customers see earlier, more accurate delivery dates.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">A significant opportunity</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Our analysis reveals an important gap:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Current situation: There&#39;s a notable difference between our delivery promise and actual delivery times</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Weekend operations: A significant portion of deliveries already happen on weekends</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Impact on sales: Our A/B tests have demonstrated that reducing the delivery promise by one business day leads to a measurable increase in conversion rate</span></li></ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">What does this mean for you?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">As a seller, you can now align your delivery promise with your carriers&#39; actual capabilities. If your shipping provider operates on Saturday and/or Sunday, you can now indicate this in your configuration.</span></p>\n<p><br><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">❌ Without weekend delivery:</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Order placed: Thursday morning</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Carrier delivery: 48 hours</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Customer sees: &quot;Delivery Monday&quot; (4 calendar days)</span></li></ul>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">✅ With weekend delivery:</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Order placed: Thursday morning</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Carrier delivery: 48 hours</span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Customer sees: &quot;Delivery Saturday&quot; (2 calendar days)</span></li></ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong>&#127919; Impact: </strong>Your product appears 2 days faster → Customers are more likely to buy from you!</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Concrete Benefits:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">✅ Shorter and more accurate delivery promise displayed to customers</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">✅ Better conversion: customers are more likely to buy when they see reduced delivery times</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">✅ More sales thanks to a competitive advantage on delivery speed</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">✅ Increased transparency: what you promise matches what you actually deliver</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">How to configure weekend deliveries in your BackOffice?</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">It&#39;s very simple! For each shipping configuration to a destination country where your carrier works on weekends:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">1. Access your Back Market BackOffice</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">2. Navigate to your shipping configurations</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><img src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0Sb0000008fnZ&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EMSb00000KDDOv\" alt=\"\" width=\"552\" height=\"195\"></img> </span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">3. Select the configuration affected by weekend deliveries</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><img src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0Sb0000008fnZ&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EMSb00000KCkEu\" alt=\"\" width=\"542\" height=\"464\"></img> </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">4. Enable working days: check Saturday and/or Sunday according to your carrier&#39;s operating days</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><img src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0Sb0000008fnZ&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EMSb00000KDDjt\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"474\"></img> </span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">5. Save your changes</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;padding-left: 40px;\"> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Our recommendations:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">✅ Check with your carriers which days they actually operate for each destination</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">✅ Enable this option only for routes where you&#39;re certain the carrier works on weekends</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Frequently asked questions :</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"></span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong><em>Q: What if my carrier only delivers on Saturday, not Sunday?</em></strong></span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><em>A: No problem! You can enable Saturday only. The system is flexible.</em></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong><em>Q: Can I disable it later if needed?</em></strong></span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><em>A: Yes, you can enable or disable weekend deliveries at any time in your BackOffice.</em></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><strong><em>Q: Which carriers typically deliver on weekends?</em></strong></span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"><em>A: Royal Mail, Colissimo, DPD, Chronopost, it depends on your contract. Check with your specific carrier.</em></span></p>"
}